snippet.title: LORDS OF THE FALLEN - Official Gameplay Reveal Trailer || Pre-Order Now on PC, PS5 & Xbox Series X|S
snippet.description:
Pre-Order Lords of the Fallen on PC, PS5 & Xbox Series X/S - https://lotfgame.info/preorder-YT

Lords of the Fallen releases Friday, October 13.

A vast world awaits in all-new, dark fantasy action-RPG, Lords of the Fallen. As one of the fabled Dark Crusaders, embark on an epic quest to overthrow Adyr, the demon God.

Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/lotfgame/
